trans-unit.source: Enables <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls or other server controls to contain collections of verbs.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverar <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller eller andra kontroller innehåller datasamlingar verb.

trans-unit.source: A verb in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls is an action that a user can carry out in the user interface (UI).
trans-unit.target: Ett verb i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller är en åtgärd som en användare kan utföra i användargränssnittet (UI).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Typically, a verb is represented in the UI by a clickable control such as a button, a link, or a menu item.
trans-unit.target: Vanligtvis visas ett verb i Användargränssnittet för en klickbar kontroll, till exempel en knapp, en länk eller ett menyalternativ.

trans-unit.source: The Web Parts control set provides standard verbs that are available by default to <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls and other server controls (such as custom, ASP.NET, and user controls) that can act like <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls when placed in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> zones.
trans-unit.target: Webbdelar kontrollen anger Standardverb som är tillgängliga som standard <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller och andra serverkontroller (till exempel anpassade, ASP.NET och användaren styr) som kan fungera som <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>styr när placeras i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>zoner.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Standard verbs include close, minimize, restore, delete, edit, and export.
trans-unit.target: Standardverb inkluderar Stäng, minimera, återställa, ta bort, redigera och exportera.

trans-unit.source: You can also create custom verbs for use with <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> and server controls.
trans-unit.target: Du kan också skapa anpassade verb för användning med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>och webbserverkontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The IWebActionable interface, with its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A> property, gives you a way to integrate custom verbs into your controls.
trans-unit.target: Gränssnittet IWebActionable med dess <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A>egenskapen ger dig ett sätt att integrera anpassade verb i kontrollerna.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class implements the IWebActionable interface and implements its single property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klassen implementerar gränssnittet IWebActionable och implementerar en enda egenskap.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: To add custom verbs to a control that inherits from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class, you must override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, add custom verbs to a collection, and return the collection.
trans-unit.target: Att lägga till anpassade verb i en kontroll som ärver från den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klass, måste du åsidosätta den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen, lägga till anpassade verb i en samling och returnera samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The collection referenced by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property contains only custom verbs; standard verbs are not included in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Den samling som refererar till den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen innehåller bara anpassade verb; standardverb ingår inte i den här samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The default return value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control is `null`, because by default there are no custom verbs in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Standard returnera värdet för den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskap i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen är `null`eftersom som standard finns inga anpassade verb i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Adding custom verbs to server controls that are not <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls requires one extra step.
trans-unit.target: Lägga till anpassade verb i kontroller som inte är <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller krävs extra steg.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: In those cases, the controls must also implement the IWebActionable interface and implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: I sådana fall måste kontrollerna även implementera gränssnittet IWebActionable och implementera den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A>

trans-unit.source: After you have added custom verbs to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A> collection, the Web Parts control set automatically handles the other steps necessary to create and render the custom verbs.
trans-unit.target: När du har lagt till anpassade verb som den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A>samling webbdelar kontrollen automatiskt hanterar steg som krävs för att skapa och göra de anpassade verb.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to a collection of custom <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en referens till en samling av anpassade <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: The Verbs property references a collection of custom verbs (if any) that are added to a verbs menu in the header of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> or other server control.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen verb refererar till en samling av anpassade verb (eventuella) som har lagts till i en meny verb i rubriken för en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>eller annan serverkontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The Verbs collection does not contain references to the standard <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb> objects provided with the Web Parts control set, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.CloseVerb%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.DeleteVerb%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.EditVerb%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.RestoreVerb%2A>, or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.MinimizeVerb%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen verb inte innehålla referenser till vanlig <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb>objekt som kontrollen webbdelar har angetts som <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.CloseVerb%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.DeleteVerb%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.EditVerb%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.RestoreVerb%2A>, eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.MinimizeVerb%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.MinimizeVerb%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.RestoreVerb%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.EditVerb%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.DeleteVerb%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.CloseVerb%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb>

trans-unit.source: Developers who want to add custom verbs to a custom control that derives from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class can simply override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A> property that the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class implements.
trans-unit.target: Utvecklare som vill lägga till anpassade verb som en anpassad kontroll som härleds från den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klassen kan helt enkelt åsidosätta den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A>egenskapen som den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klassen implementerar.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Developers who want to add custom verbs to a user control, or a custom control that is not a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, must implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable> interface by providing an implementation of the Verbs property.
trans-unit.target: Utvecklare som vill lägga till anpassade verb i en användarkontroll eller en anpassad kontroll som inte är en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>styra, måste implementera den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable>gränssnittet genom att tillhandahålla en implementering av egenskapen verb.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerbCollection"></xref> that contains custom <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerbCollection"> </xref> som innehåller anpassade <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"> </xref> objekt.
